sentence: how many first class flights does united have leaving from all airports today
sq2:
SELECT  COUNT(*), '"'||v0.airline_code||'"' FROM flight v0 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = 'UA') AND ((v0.from_airport IN (
SELECT v1.airport_code FROM airport v1 
WHERE ( 1 =  1))) AND ((v0.flight_days IN (
SELECT v2.days_code FROM days v2 
WHERE (v2.day_name IN (
SELECT v3.day_name FROM date_day v3 
WHERE (((v3.year =  1993) 
AND (v3.month_number =  4)) AND (v3.day_number =  29)))))) 
AND (v0.flight_id IN (
SELECT v4.flight_id FROM flight_fare v4 
WHERE (v4.fare_id IN (
SELECT v5.fare_id FROM fare v5 
WHERE ((v5.fare_basis_code IN (
SELECT v6.fare_basis_code FROM fare_basis v6 
WHERE (v6.class_type = 'FIRST'))) 
AND (v5.fare_basis_code IN (
SELECT v7.fare_basis_code FROM fare_basis v7 
WHERE (v7.basis_days IN (
SELECT v8.days_code FROM days v8 
WHERE (v8.day_name IN (
SELECT v9.day_name FROM date_day v9 
WHERE (((v9.year =  1993) AND (v9.month_number =  4)) 
AND (v9.day_number =  29)))))))))))))))) GROUP BY v0.airline_code;
